  "texts": [
    "Based on the course's achievement outcomes from prior semesters, Dien et al (2020) established for predicting student performance in the upcoming semesters.",
    "This was accomplished by analyzing and presenting several pre-processing strategies (such as Quantile Transforms and MinMax Scaler) before DL models such as LSTM and CNN were used to collect the data.",
    "The model was additionally modified to include other optimizer functions, such as Adam and RMSprop, to enhance prediction performance.",
    "A student information system from Vietnamese interdisciplinary university was used to acquire four million samples for the experiments, which were constructed using 16 datasets connected to a wide range of different disciplines.",
    "The results indicated that the proposed strategy, particularly when employing data modification, produced accurate prediction results."
  ],
  "correct_citations": [
    "Based on the course's achievement outcomes from prior semesters, Dien et al (2020) established for predicting student performance in the upcoming semesters."
  ]
